snippet.title: Deeper than the Ocean Official Trailer (2018) Gal Gadot, Amber Heard, Drama Movie HD
snippet.description:
The beautiful story about two women who loved each other more than someone could ever imagine. Mera (Amber Heard) and Diana (Gal Gadot) had to break up due to the laws of Xebel, Mera's kingdom and home, and the duty of being Wonder Woman. But they can't simply forget each other and the world will cross their paths only one more time.

---------
